## 🎨 Design Decisions

### Color Coding
Each FAQ category has a unique color to aid visual scanning:
- **Blue** (Supported Formats) - Technical/informational
- **Amber** (Failed Prints & Refunds) - Warning/caution
- **Emerald** (Privacy & Security) - Trust/safety
- **Purple** (General) - Neutral/miscellaneous

### Accordion Behavior
- Only one answer visible at a time per section (no "expand all")
- Smooth height animations (250ms)
- Chevron rotates 180° when opened
- Click anywhere on question to toggle

### Navigation
- **Back button** returns to previous page (uses `navigate(-1)`)
- **Logo** in top nav (non-clickable, decorative)
- No authentication required - public access

